CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 28, 1951, pg. 23 reads: "Baby Contest Winners - Here are the winners of the Baby Contest sponsored by the Gospel Choir of Bethel AME Church last Sunday. They are, left to right: James Snowden, first prize winner; Mary Hunter, second prize winner, and Victor Gardner, third prize winner. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Winners of baby contest, from left: James Snowden, Mary Hunter, and Victor Gardner, sponsored by the Gospel Choir of Bethel AME Church
